talk-spotter (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add Vosk grammar constraints for improved command recognition accuracy
  * Remove --spot-mode flag; spotting is now always enabled
  * Add --no-grammar flag to disable vocabulary constraints
  * Add "complete" as an alternative to "end" for finishing commands
  * Fix voice command parsing when entire command is spoken in one utterance
  * Fix premature timeout caused by partial results being fed to command parser
  * Fix frequency not being parsed when spoken in the same utterance as "end"

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Thu, 06 Mar 2026 12:00:00 -0500

talk-spotter (0.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add POTA spot posting support
  * Add SOTA spot posting support with OAuth authentication
  * Fix RTL-SDR freezing by separating read and process threads
  * Add slow AGC to smooth audio level variations
  * Add DC offset removal to FM demodulator
  * Add second model path option to config
  * Enhance error handling in SOTA authentication

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Sun, 02 Feb 2026 12:00:00 -0500

talk-spotter (0.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * KiwiSDR and RTL-SDR support
  * Voice command parsing with DX Cluster posting
  * Live transcription mode

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Wed, 29 Jan 2026 12:00:00 -0500
